The NHSquicker app has 3 main features:

title: About the App
text:
About the App
NHSquicker is a free app which provides live wait time information for NHS services in Devon, Cornwall and Somerset. It was developed to improve patient access to NHS services by providing a reliable, easy-to-use platform to manage healthcare needs.


What the App Does
The app has multiple features, including:

View live wait times
Find alternative services, such as GP and pharmacies
Access information on health conditions and treatments

NHSquicker is a free app which provides live wait times for NHS services in Devon, Cornwall and Somerset.

Helps people choose the right service for them.
Helps relieve the pressure off the NHS.


A&E waiting times have increased substantially over recent years.
NHSquicker was created to guide people to choose the appropriate service for them, steering away from unnecessary visits to A&E departments.
